1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:12,130
Three easy ways to cure intelligence excusitis are, number one, never underestimate your own intelligence and never overestimate the intelligence of others.

2
00:00:12,320 --> 00:00:14,210
Don't sell yourself short.

3
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:16,289
Concentrate on your assets.

4
00:00:16,480 --> 00:00:18,770
Discover your superior talents.

5
00:00:19,039 --> 00:00:22,849
Remember, it's not how many brains you've got that matters.

6
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:26,210
Rather, it's how you use your brains that counts.

7
00:00:26,720 --> 00:00:31,569
Manage your brains instead of worrying about how much IQ you've got.

8
00:00:32,559 --> 00:00:33,650
2.

9
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:40,609
Remind yourself several times daily, my attitudes are more important than my intelligence.

10
00:00:40,880 --> 00:00:44,770
At work and at home, practice positive attitudes.

11
00:00:45,039 --> 00:00:49,569
See the reasons why you can do it, not the reasons why you can't.

12
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:52,690
Develop an I'm winning attitude.

13
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:56,210
Put your intelligence to creative positive use.

14
00:00:56,480 --> 00:01:01,010
Use it to find ways to win, not to prove you will lose.

15
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,250
3.

16
00:01:03,680 --> 00:01:10,289
Remember that the ability to think is of much greater value than the ability to memorize facts.

17
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:16,930
Use your mind to create and develop ideas, to find new and better ways to do things.

18
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:26,210
Ask yourself, am I using my mental ability to make history, or am I using it merely to record history made by others?

